                    "acceptedAnswer": {
                        "@type": "Answer",
                        "text": "At a glance, the 11 GICS stock market sectors are:EnergyMaterialsIndustrialsUtilitiesHealthcareFinancialsConsumer DiscretionaryConsumer StaplesInformation TechnologyCommunication ServicesReal Estate",
