<section class="block-paragraph">
<h3 data-block-key="vmwnt">6. Financials Sector</h3><p data-block-key="njxmp">The financials sector includes businesses that are primarily related to handling money. Banks are a key industry group within the sector, but you&#x27;ll also find insurance companies, brokerage houses, consumer finance providers, and mortgage-related real estate investment trusts among financials.</p><p data-block-key="yaf0x">Warren Buffett&#x27;s <b>Berkshire Hathaway</b> (<span class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap" data-id="206249"><a href="/quote/nyse/brk.a/">BRK.A</a> <span class="text-green-900 ticker-change"> 0.19%</span></span>) (<span class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap" data-id="206602"><a href="/quote/nyse/brk.b/">BRK.B</a> <span class="text-red-900 ticker-change"> -1.0%</span></span>) and financial giant <b>JPMorgan Chase</b> (<span class="font-bold whitespace-nowrap" data-id="204149"><a href="/quote/nyse/jpm/">JPM</a> <span class="text-red-900 ticker-change"> -1.37%</span></span>) are among the best-known stocks in the financials sector.</p><h2 data-block-key="cosp4">More on these sectors</h2>
</section>
