<div class="qna-content">
<p data-block-key="652er">At a glance, the 11 GICS stock market sectors are:</p><ol><li data-block-key="ca3am"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/energy/">Energy</a></li><li data-block-key="cqgew"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/materials/">Materials</a></li><li data-block-key="mawn2"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/industrials/">Industrials</a></li><li data-block-key="rgcmk"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/utilities/">Utilities</a></li><li data-block-key="qzyt8"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/healthcare/">Healthcare</a></li><li data-block-key="n5dmw"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/financials/">Financials</a></li><li data-block-key="yizr3"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/consumer-discretionary/">Consumer Discretionary</a></li><li data-block-key="860lh"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/consumer-staples/">Consumer Staples</a></li><li data-block-key="u7ti9"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/information-technology/">Information Technology</a></li><li data-block-key="ffuch"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/communication/">Communication Services</a></li><li data-block-key="p5liz"><a href="/investing/stock-market/market-sectors/real-estate-investing/best-stocks/">Real Estate</a></li></ol>
